    <item>
      <title>监管机构瞄准科技行业 谷歌和苹果分拆提上日程</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/google-apple-breakups-agenda-global-regulators-target-tech-2024-03-24/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着大西洋两岸的反垄断监管机构严厉打击所谓的反竞争行为，大型科技公司正面临数十年来的最大挑战，这些行为可能导致苹果和 Alphabet 旗下的谷歌收到分拆令，这在该行业尚属首次。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/google-apple-breakups-agenda-global-regulators-target-tech-2024-03-24/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 01:04:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
